      "comment": "LARA DUTTON (8) is a sprinter who thrives over these shorter races. Filled the minor placings over 411m at this track (23.72) in a Mix 1/2/3 but is better placed at the shorter trip here. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Speedy runner who can find the front with a clear break from out wide. One of the leading chances. OSCAR DUTTON (4) was out of character last run when missing the frame, finishing sixth (17.49) in a NG at this track. Normally safely away but always well back and facing a task from wide out last time. Form here at this distance is sound. Worth another chance. ZIPPING SPARTAN (1) will run well despite no experience on this track.",
